{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 89746, "create_time": 1651126858, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "这TM是小学题？", "timestamp": 1651126858}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 89747, "create_time": 1651126910, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: Alice觉得应该是什么难度的题呢？虽然我感觉其中必有蹊跷", "timestamp": 1651126910}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 89748, "create_time": 1651126920, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: ？", "timestamp": 1651126920}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 89749, "create_time": 1651126985, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "小学生会算正四棱锥两个面的夹角？", "timestamp": 1651126985}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 89750, "create_time": 1651127062, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "为啥会有人选5？", "timestamp": 1651127062}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 89752, "create_time": 1651127136, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Eve: 我感觉答案可能就是5，因为可能是共面的，需要计算夹角，不能想当然就选7", "timestamp": 1651127136}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 89754, "create_time": 1651127142, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Eve: 因为他们认为有两组三角形拼接后分别在同一平面上", "timestamp": 1651127142}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 89757, "create_time": 1651127389, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Eve: 难道不是5？", "timestamp": 1651127389}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 89762, "create_time": 1651127527, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Carol: 那里有两个全等三角形所以平面夹角相同", "timestamp": 1651127527}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 89777, "create_time": 1651129328, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "顶楞和底面两条棱平行且等长，所以前（后）面的两个三角形共面，形成一个平行四边形", "timestamp": 1651129328}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 89812, "create_time": 1651131800, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "看过一个故事，大家都认为是7，结果是五", "timestamp": 1651131800}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 89831, "create_time": 1651133891, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "高中数学老师讲过，推了一通最后三棱锥的一个面和四棱锥的一个面共面（图上看大概就是a的后面的那个面)", "timestamp": 1651133891}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 90039, "create_time": 1651143407, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "不算不知道，这两个面竟然是共面的", "timestamp": 1651143407}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 90319, "create_time": 1651154502, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "想象一个由每条边都为1的边搭起来的的三棱斜柱，此时它并不稳定，需要固定，于是从底面两个点往上面对角的点又拉了两条长为1的边固定。就形成了第三个图。所以反过来说二者结合后本来就是三棱斜柱", "timestamp": 1651154502}], "create_time": 1651126687, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": true, "last_comment_time": 1651154502, "likenum": 13, "n_attentions": 13, "n_comments": 14, "pid": 32814, "poll": {"answers": [{"option": "5", "votes": 30}, {"option": "6", "votes": 3}, {"option": "7", "votes": 65}, {"option": "8", "votes": 0}, {"option": "🍉", "votes": 12}], "vote": null}, "reply": 14, "text": "#小学数学题\n然而据说大部分人会选错\n现有各棱长均相等的一个正三棱锥和一个正四棱锥，当将它们的一